---
title: Shepherd's Pie with Spring Onion Mash and Green Beans
description: This Shepherd's Pie with Spring Onion Mash is bursting full of flavours and make the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh. Cook up a fresh start!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/shepherds-pie-4a02ffe5-13a20f97.jpg
